        <div class="figure">
          <img src="/manuals/foredom-sr/p04_06.png" alt="Handpiece connection detail" />
          <figcaption>Connection detail</figcaption>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ol>
        <li>Hold the black metal outer sheath tip facing upward.</li>
        <li>Turn on the motor to about half speed and allow it to slow down.</li>
        <li>While the inner key tip is still rotating, grip the handpiece and push it onto the sheath tip with one firm motion until it snaps into place.</li>
        <li>Verify by inserting and tightening an accessory, then running at low speed &mdash; the accessory should rotate smoothly.</li>
      </ol>

