        <li>Hang M.SR motors 30&Prime;&ndash;40&Prime; above the work surface.</li>
        <li>Position to the right of the work if right-handed, or to the left if left-handed.</li>
        <li>Use a safety clip or hook to prevent the motor from jumping or twisting off an open hook at start-up. Foredom motor hangers include a safety clip.</li>
        <li>If using an open hook, secure the motor with wire or heavy tape.</li>
